fields.name: Mode
fields.description: When Force, any existing target tags will be overwritten. When NoForce, any existing target tags will fail the operation before any copying begins.

fields.name: TargetTags
fields.description: List of strings of the form repo[:tag]. When tag is omitted the source will be used (or 'latest' if source tag is also omitted).

fields.name: UntaggedTargetRepositories
fields.description: List of strings of repository names to do a manifest only copy. No tag will be created.
